'''Raymond Lucas''' (13 December 1918 &ndash; 15 December 2006)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siteducyclisme.net/coureurfiche.php?coureurid=26995 |title=Raymond Lucas |work=siteducyclisme.net |accessdate=12 January 2019}}</ref> was a French [[bicycle racing|racing cyclist]]. He rode in the [[1947 Tour de France|1947]] and [[1949 Tour de France]].<ref name="CyclingArchives">{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingarchives.com/coureurfiche.php?coureurid=26995 |title=Raymond Lucas |accessdate=25 April 2014 |work=Cycling Archives}}</ref><ref name="ProCycling">{{cite web |url=http://www.procyclingstats.com/rider.php?id=172828 |title=Raymond Lucas |accessdate=25 April 2014 |work=ProCyclingStats}}</ref><ref name="mdc1949">{{cite web|url=http://memoire-du-cyclisme.net/eta_tdf_1947_1977/tdf1949.php|publisher=Memoire du cyclisme|title=36Ã¨me Tour de France 1949|language=French|accessdate=8 March 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124102917/http://www.memoire-du-cyclisme.net/eta_tdf_1947_1977/tdf1949.php|archivedate=24 January 2012}}</ref>

